             sworn.</p>
               <p>I was coming by, and saw a <rs id="t17830604-34-deflabel175" type="occupation">boy</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t17830604-34-defend386 t17830604-34-deflabel175"></join> coming out of Mr. Marridge's house with some linen under his hat, I knocked at the door, and told Mrs. Marridge she was robbed, he walked away and was pursued directly.</p>
               <p>
            
